LEX Escrow


"Payer" is a person

"Payee" is a person

"Arbiter" is a person

"Amount" is an amount


The Payer pays an Amount into escrow, appoints the Payee, appoints the Arbiter


CLAUSE: Pay Out

The Arbiter may pay the escrow to the Payee


CLAUSE: Pay Back

The Arbiter may pay the escrow to the Payer


